	   <tr><td colspan=2>CHA is not important to a Necro at all. It has nothing to do with successful fear or spell hits. I am a 61 Iksar necro and my CHA is 18. Very very rarely does my fear not hit or my spells get resisted. If CHA were necessary for this to be true then I would still be level 8. Please don't steer upcoming necros the wrong way. Fellow bonecasters screw CHA, build that mana pool. However, things do cost quite a bit more at the vendor.<br><br>Razorheart Bloodreaver<br>61 Warlock of Cazic<br>E-Marr<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
